attributionInfo.agentName: Talk to Tina Low, Christina 'Tina' Low

data.description: Nestled in North Joplin's most established and sought after neighborhood, 1232 Bramar offers everything a growing family could need!  Enjoy entertaining in the large great room with a soaring vaulted ceiling and an ample amount of natural light provided by the casement windows. These features compliment the brick, gas fireplace wonderfully. Enjoy the chef's dream kitchen with a gas cooktop, granite countertops, plenty of storage space and even a pot filler! Easy clean-up with central vac through the home with an accessible vent in the kitchen! This space opens to a beautiful backyard featuring a brand new pergola, and lots of landscaping. Also on the main floor, you'll find a huge primary suite with a large bathroom and closets, 2 additional bedrooms with a private bath, a formal dining space, and a designated office- perfect for remote work! The basement offers a HUGE family room perfect for entertaining as well as more bedrooms, bathrooms, storage, and a secure safe room! Don't miss your chance to see this beautiful home!
